290
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:49,160
How can you be sure it's human blood?

291
00:23:51,880 --> 00:23:53,350
Chief Zhang, Captain Wang,

292
00:23:53,350 --> 00:23:55,440
Lang Bowen was beaten up at Fenglinwan.

293
00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:56,100
Who did it?

294
00:23:56,270 --> 00:23:57,550
We're still looking into the details.

295
00:23:57,550 --> 00:24:00,350
Lang Bowen has been sent
to the People's Hospital.

296
00:24:00,920 --> 00:24:01,880
Should we go there?

297
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:02,540
Yes.

298
00:24:02,740 --> 00:24:03,640
I'll go there with Li Qian.

299
00:24:03,640 --> 00:24:04,440
You two keep an eye on things here.

300
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:04,770
Okay.

301
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:10,370
Doubt the doubt of the doubt.

302
00:24:10,680 --> 00:24:11,400
Get to work.

303
00:24:12,750 --> 00:24:14,410
What are you wondering about?

304
00:24:17,160 --> 00:24:18,160
What do you think?

305
00:24:19,030 --> 00:24:20,720
Let's assume that Liu Bei is really dead.

306
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:21,720
It must have something to do

307
00:24:21,720 --> 00:24:22,480
with the transaction

308
00:24:22,480 --> 00:24:24,010
in Zhou Rong's villa today.

309
00:24:24,270 --> 00:24:25,200
What do you mean?

310
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:27,440
This method is too professional.

311
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:29,030
It's not like the work of ordinary people.

312
00:24:29,030 --> 00:24:30,070
The only ones I can think of

313
00:24:30,070 --> 00:24:31,270
are Zhou Rong's gang.

314
00:24:32,310 --> 00:24:33,840
It might also be the seller.

315
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:36,000
After all, anyone who dares
to resell bianzhong

316
00:24:36,000 --> 00:24:37,660
is surely no ordinary person.

317
00:24:39,110 --> 00:24:39,830
Why

318
00:24:41,110 --> 00:24:42,270
couldn't it be that Liu Bei

319
00:24:42,270 --> 00:24:43,470
killed the other one?

320
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:45,030
That's unlikely.

321
00:24:45,550 --> 00:24:46,950
Liu Bei was being hunted.

322
00:24:47,750 --> 00:24:49,200
Even if he killed someone,

323
00:24:49,200 --> 00:24:50,310
he wouldn't spend so much effort

324
00:24:50,310 --> 00:24:51,570
cleaning up the scene.

325
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:53,080
Escaping mattered more.

326
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:54,400
But

327
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:56,480
Zhou Rong or Zhu Yifei's gang

328
00:24:57,310 --> 00:24:58,480
would do this to cover their tracks

329
00:24:58,480 --> 00:24:59,200
and continue

330
00:24:59,200 --> 00:25:00,200
the transaction.

331
00:25:00,400 --> 00:25:01,070
Therefore,

332
00:25:02,590 --> 00:25:04,000
can this case now be merged

333
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:05,930
and handled with Zhou Rong's case?

334
00:25:07,920 --> 00:25:09,200
That's for the higher-ups to decide.

335
00:25:09,200 --> 00:25:10,930
I wouldn't dare to say too much.

336
00:25:13,550 --> 00:25:15,280
You're very meticulous, girl.

337
00:25:32,880 --> 00:25:34,760
Why are you sighing?

338
00:25:35,880 --> 00:25:36,720
I just drank too much

339
00:25:36,720 --> 00:25:38,230
and got into a fight.

340
00:25:38,510 --> 00:25:39,550
It's nothing.

341
00:25:40,110 --> 00:25:41,240
Hurry up and go home.

342
00:25:42,070 --> 00:25:43,550
I'll stay here with you tonight.

343
00:25:43,550 --> 00:25:45,010
Why would you stay with me?

344
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:46,480
Can you give injections

345
00:25:46,480 --> 00:25:47,680
or change dressings?

346
00:25:48,830 --> 00:25:50,270
What if you need
to use the bathroom at night?

347
00:25:50,270 --> 00:25:51,570
There are so many people outside.

348
00:25:51,570 --> 00:25:53,030
I don't need you to help me.

349
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:54,510
Just leave now.

350
00:25:55,880 --> 00:25:56,380
Bowen,

351
00:25:56,640 --> 00:25:57,840
Zhang Yi'ang is here.

352
00:26:01,350 --> 00:26:02,510
Hurry! Go to the bathroom!

353
00:26:02,510 --> 00:26:04,170
Hide in the bathroom for a bit.

354
00:26:11,590 --> 00:26:13,050
Did we go to the wrong room?

355
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:17,340
Chief Zhang.

356
00:26:17,680 --> 00:26:18,410
Oh, it's you.

357
00:26:19,440 --> 00:26:20,160
Officer Li.

358
00:26:20,790 --> 00:26:21,650
What happened?

359
00:26:21,660 --> 00:26:23,270
I've been waiting for you.

360
00:26:23,640 --> 00:26:24,440
What's wrong?

361
00:26:24,590 --> 00:26:26,050
I got beaten up by someone.

362
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:27,200
You got beaten up?

363
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:28,850
By whom?

364
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:30,730
How many of them were there?

365
00:26:32,590 --> 00:26:33,610
Two.

366
00:26:33,750 --> 00:26:34,510
Two.

367
00:26:34,750 --> 00:26:37,520
[Patient's bedside card]
[Name: Lang Bowen]

368
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:39,550
Three.

369
00:26:42,200 --> 00:26:43,460
Four.

370
00:26:43,590 --> 00:26:44,910
Five? Or six?

371
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:45,880
Lang Bowen,

372
00:26:46,590 --> 00:26:47,590
we don't have time

373
00:26:47,590 --> 00:26:49,190
to joke around with you here.

374
00:26:50,960 --> 00:26:52,070
Look at me.

375
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:56,220
I'm in no mood to joke around with you.

376
00:27:06,270 --> 00:27:07,000
Chief Zhang.

377
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:10,830
I don't know
if it's because I drank too much

378
00:27:10,830 --> 00:27:12,110
or if it's from the beating

379
00:27:12,110 --> 00:27:13,840
that I might have a concussion.

380
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:15,930
When I look at you now,

381
00:27:17,110 --> 00:27:18,480
I see double.

382
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:21,310
D-Don't move.

383
00:27:21,350 --> 00:27:22,400
If you move, I see four.

384
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:23,310
Oh, no, I feel nauseous.

385
00:27:23,310 --> 00:27:24,110
Nauseous?

386
00:27:24,960 --> 00:27:25,680
Did you also not see clearly

387
00:27:25,680 --> 00:27:26,940
what they looked like?

388
00:27:27,750 --> 00:27:29,050
Let me think.

389
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:30,640
Take your time to recall.

390
00:27:32,270 --> 00:27:33,480
I didn't see clearly.

391
00:27:36,680 --> 00:27:38,880
Fenglinwan has surveillance cameras.

392
00:27:39,240 --> 00:27:41,570
You can go ask Lu Yibo
to check the footage.

393
00:27:41,830 --> 00:27:42,960
Since it's about me,

394
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:45,340
he wouldn't dare take it lightly.

395
00:27:47,830 --> 00:27:48,510
Oh, right.

396
00:27:49,550 --> 00:27:51,350
The surveillance system was upgraded
last night.

397
00:27:51,350 --> 00:27:52,590
All cameras in Fenglinwan

398
00:27:52,590 --> 00:27:53,790
were down for 2 hours.

399
00:27:55,240 --> 00:27:55,830
For real?

400
00:27:57,510 --> 00:27:58,200
For real.

401
00:28:01,310 --> 00:28:02,270
You've checked?

402
00:28:04,790 --> 00:28:05,590
Get well soon.

403
00:28:05,720 --> 00:28:06,320
Rest well.

404
00:28:07,310 --> 00:28:08,040
Chief Zhang,

405
00:28:08,270 --> 00:28:10,480
you can't just leave like this.

406
00:28:10,510 --> 00:28:11,240
Chief Zhang,

407
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:12,880
I was beaten up like this

408
00:28:12,880 --> 00:28:14,430
for no reason.

409
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:17,860
You can't just
ask several questions and leave.

410
00:28:18,550 --> 00:28:20,170
You can't do this to me.

411
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:20,750
Let go.

412
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:21,960
We can talk properly.

413
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:22,760
Let go of me.

414
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:23,820
Chief Zhang,

415
00:28:24,160 --> 00:28:25,480
who beat me up?

416
00:28:26,310 --> 00:28:27,920
Why did they do this to me?

417
00:28:28,510 --> 00:28:29,830
I won't dare to go out

418
00:28:30,680 --> 00:28:32,210
until this is figured out.

419
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:32,970
Chief Zhang,

420
00:28:33,680 --> 00:28:36,200
is this still a society ruled by law?

421
00:28:36,270 --> 00:28:37,550
Did you notice anything?

422
00:28:37,550 --> 00:28:39,680
He's injured, but still quite strong.

423
00:28:45,070 --> 00:28:48,590
You can't do this to me.

424
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:51,260
A wasted trip.

425
00:28:56,550 --> 00:28:57,350
What's wrong?

426
00:28:58,350 --> 00:28:58,880
Two.

427
00:29:01,480 --> 00:29:03,680
There should be two people who beat him.

428
00:29:04,050 --> 00:29:04,640
He paused for a second

429
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:05,510
and then said three or four.

430
00:29:05,510 --> 00:29:06,350
He said three or four

431
00:29:06,350 --> 00:29:07,410
just to confuse us.

432
00:29:08,240 --> 00:29:09,770
The truth is in the details.

433
00:29:10,510 --> 00:29:11,270
And when he talked about

434
00:29:11,270 --> 00:29:12,030
the people who hit him,

435
00:29:12,030 --> 00:29:13,030
he said "they."

436
00:29:13,680 --> 00:29:14,790
"They" means it wasn't just one person.

437
00:29:14,790 --> 00:29:16,350
Most likely, there were two.

438
00:29:16,350 --> 00:29:17,720
Zhou Rong was also robbed by two people.

439
00:29:17,720 --> 00:29:18,270
Could these two

440
00:29:18,270 --> 00:29:19,000
be those two?

441
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:21,720
"They" could also mean three or four.

442
00:29:21,720 --> 00:29:22,480
Five or six.

443
00:29:22,790 --> 00:29:23,350
See?

444
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,110
Why must it be two?

445
00:29:28,310 --> 00:29:29,370
I told you

446
00:29:29,680 --> 00:29:30,970
he said two at first,

447
00:29:31,070 --> 00:29:31,930
then paused,

448
00:29:31,960 --> 00:29:33,220
and said three or four.

449
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:35,130
He said three or four

450
00:29:35,550 --> 00:29:37,080
just in order to confuse us.

451
00:29:37,920 --> 00:29:39,180
These are the details.

452
00:30:09,270 --> 00:30:10,830
Eight pieces.

453
00:30:13,640 --> 00:30:14,410
Uncle.

454
00:30:15,400 --> 00:30:16,600
Everything's ready.

455
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:19,940
Where is the stuff?

456
00:30:23,720 --> 00:30:24,930
I already got it.

457
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:27,060
I put Liu Bei's body

458
00:30:27,070 --> 00:30:28,310
in the box for the bianzhong

459
00:30:28,310 --> 00:30:29,110
to bring back.

460
00:30:30,790 --> 00:30:32,410
I went outside to take a taxi.

461
00:30:33,310 --> 00:30:34,970
Just as I put the box in the car,

462
00:30:35,880 --> 00:30:37,070
the driver ran away.

463
00:30:42,480 --> 00:30:44,640
Oh, my god.

464
00:30:46,160 --> 00:30:46,880
Zheng,

465
00:30:47,480 --> 00:30:49,370
you got robbed

466
00:30:49,400 --> 00:30:50,330
by a taxi driver?

467
00:30:50,830 --> 00:30:51,920
It definitely wasn't

468
00:30:51,920 --> 00:30:52,990
an ordinary taxi driver!

469
00:30:52,990 --> 00:30:54,850
He must be Zhou Rong's man, Uncle!

470
00:31:07,510 --> 00:31:08,290
Uncle,

471
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:10,880
shouldn't we make some preparations?

472
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:11,790
Prepare for what?

473
00:31:11,790 --> 00:31:13,000
Take our weapons!

474
00:31:14,920 --> 00:31:15,450
For what?

475
00:31:15,830 --> 00:31:16,890
To fight Zhou Rong.

476
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:22,400
Zheng, Zheng.

477
00:31:23,920 --> 00:31:26,200
Some things shouldn't be rushed.

478
00:31:28,510 --> 00:31:29,270
Hang it up

479
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:31,750
and let the wind blow.

480
00:31:37,070 --> 00:31:38,070
Let's go to sleep.

481
00:31:39,750 --> 00:31:41,300
Let the wind blow?

482
00:31:48,350 --> 00:31:49,720
So many people in Fenglinwan

483
00:31:49,720 --> 00:31:51,120
couldn't stop these two?

484
00:31:51,590 --> 00:31:53,720
Both of them were too good at fighting.

485
00:31:53,790 --> 00:31:55,110
So you tried to stop them but failed.

486
00:31:55,110 --> 00:31:56,310
By the time we got the news,

487
00:31:56,310 --> 00:31:57,770
they had already run away.

488
00:31:58,160 --> 00:31:59,460
Yibo!

489
00:31:59,750 --> 00:32:01,130
Bowen is one of our own.

490
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:03,160
We should've looked out for him
on our turf!

491
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:03,720
Rong,

492
00:32:04,200 --> 00:32:05,130
you have no idea.

493
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:06,370
Lang Bowen was drunk

494
00:32:06,510 --> 00:32:08,310
and stirred up trouble
in every private room.

495
00:32:08,310 --> 00:32:08,790
Other than you,

496
00:32:08,790 --> 00:32:10,920
who else could keep him under control?

497
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:13,110
Are you saying

498
00:32:13,720 --> 00:32:14,940
Bowen asked for it?

499
00:32:15,810 --> 00:32:17,020
Exactly.

500
00:32:17,440 --> 00:32:19,170
He just ran into two tough guys.

501
00:32:21,590 --> 00:32:22,160
Mr. Zhou,

502
00:32:22,830 --> 00:32:24,370
if you had been there,

503
00:32:24,640 --> 00:32:26,030
I would have definitely
fought them to the death!

504
00:32:26,030 --> 00:32:26,920
Save it!

505
00:32:27,790 --> 00:32:28,650
Mr. Zhou.

506
00:32:29,590 --> 00:32:30,390
We found them.

507
00:32:31,830 --> 00:32:32,400
Look.

508
00:32:33,070 --> 00:32:34,470
This is the clearest one.

509
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:38,060
Look, the ones who came to your house
and beat...

510
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:42,780
There's nothing else. You can leave.

511
00:32:43,110 --> 00:32:44,340
I-I'll get going.

512
00:32:47,720 --> 00:32:49,040
The ones who came to your house
and beat you up last time

513
00:32:47,940 --> 00:32:51,240
[Lobby 1]

514
00:32:49,070 --> 00:32:50,600
were also these two, right?

515
00:32:51,480 --> 00:32:54,740
I'd recognize those two
even if they were reduced to ashes.

516
00:32:55,110 --> 00:32:56,030
Right after snatching the phone,

517
00:32:56,030 --> 00:32:57,630
they went to find Lang Bowen.

518
00:32:58,270 --> 00:33:00,800
They must be trying
to get the phone password.

519
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:03,550
Last night, Du Cong was

520
00:33:03,550 --> 00:33:05,510
hit right after leaving the company.

521
00:33:05,510 --> 00:33:06,550
Du Cong said

522
00:33:06,680 --> 00:33:07,700
the ones who hit him this time

523
00:33:07,700 --> 00:33:09,620
are the same ones from last time.

524
00:33:10,440 --> 00:33:11,810
The car he drove last time

525
00:33:11,810 --> 00:33:13,540
was the one you usually ride in.

526
00:33:14,440 --> 00:33:15,970
They wanted to mess with me?

527
00:33:17,250 --> 00:33:18,930
Could it be Zhu Yifei?

528
00:33:19,550 --> 00:33:21,590
But what's in it
for an antique trafficker like him?

529
00:33:21,590 --> 00:33:23,990
It definitely has something to do
with him.

530
00:33:24,350 --> 00:33:25,420
Could it be that

531
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:27,830
someone is pulling the strings behind him?

532
00:33:27,830 --> 00:33:29,030
I don't care who it is.

533
00:33:29,880 --> 00:33:32,880
Who was the last person in Sanjiangkou
to mess with me?

534
00:33:33,270 --> 00:33:33,800
Lu Zheng.

535
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:36,830
Even the Chief
of the Public Security Bureau is gone.

536
00:33:36,830 --> 00:33:39,030
Why would I fear an antique trafficker?

537
00:33:40,550 --> 00:33:41,350
I'll take some men right now

538
00:33:41,350 --> 00:33:42,410
to find Zhu Yifei.

539
00:33:43,160 --> 00:33:43,960
Wait a minute.

540
00:33:46,240 --> 00:33:47,100
Have Li Penggai

541
00:33:47,510 --> 00:33:48,510
go find the phone.

542
00:33:49,550 --> 00:33:50,410
You come with me

543
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:52,290
to visit Lang Bowen.

544
00:33:54,310 --> 00:33:54,880
Okay.

545
00:33:55,410 --> 00:33:59,490
[Sanjiangkou People's Hospital]

546
00:34:06,200 --> 00:34:06,730
Mr. Zhou.

547
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:07,830
Mr. Zhou.

548
00:34:08,510 --> 00:34:09,230
Stay still.

549
00:34:24,630 --> 00:34:25,190
Well.

550
00:34:25,960 --> 00:34:26,489
Mr. Zhou.

551
00:34:27,190 --> 00:34:28,070
How are you doing?

552
00:34:28,070 --> 00:34:28,550
I...

553
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:31,670
It hurts.

554
00:34:34,920 --> 00:34:37,250
I just had the doctor
give me a painkiller.

555
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:40,330
You're in high spirits.

556
00:34:41,630 --> 00:34:43,150
Seems like you're not hurt too badly.

557
00:34:43,150 --> 00:34:44,210
I have a bone crack.

558
00:34:44,710 --> 00:34:46,610
The doctor said I need to improve
my blood circulation

559
00:34:46,610 --> 00:34:47,739
to recover quickly.

560
00:34:47,840 --> 00:34:49,150
Watching this can speed up

561
00:34:49,150 --> 00:34:50,409
my blood circulation.

562
00:34:51,440 --> 00:34:52,570
Did you get an X-ray?

563
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:53,400
Yes, I did.

564
00:34:54,400 --> 00:34:55,360
Mr. Zhou, Ren, you're here.

565
00:34:55,360 --> 00:34:56,150
Yangyang.

566
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:57,510
Why are you here again?

567
00:34:57,510 --> 00:34:58,570
I brought you food.

568
00:35:00,230 --> 00:35:01,960
Bring out the X-ray film for me.

569
00:35:06,170 --> 00:35:07,430
Here you are, Mr. Zhou.

570
00:35:07,550 --> 00:35:08,680
Read that report

571
00:35:08,840 --> 00:35:09,760
to Mr. Zhou.

572
00:35:11,580 --> 00:35:12,870
[Scan Report]

573
00:35:11,880 --> 00:35:13,140
Imaging findings show

574
00:35:13,150 --> 00:35:15,400
a proximal diaphyseal fracture
of the lower leg.

575
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:16,760
The fracture line is transverse

576
00:35:16,760 --> 00:35:18,480
and located in the middle of the tibia.

577
00:35:18,480 --> 00:35:20,110
The fracture line is clearly visible.

578
00:35:20,110 --> 00:35:22,110
Both ends
of the fracture are well-aligned

579
00:35:22,110 --> 00:35:23,670
with no obvious dislocation.

580
00:35:23,670 --> 00:35:26,480
No abnormalities are seen
in the surrounding soft tissue.

581
00:35:26,480 --> 00:35:27,440
Didn't you say it was a bone crack?

582
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:28,590
How come it is a fracture now?

583
00:35:28,590 --> 00:35:29,650
It doesn't matter.

584
00:35:30,550 --> 00:35:32,150
How long will it take to heal?

585
00:35:33,920 --> 00:35:35,420
A bone injury like this

586
00:35:35,630 --> 00:35:37,160
will take at least 100 days.

587
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:42,350
You see,

588
00:35:42,670 --> 00:35:44,870
I can't move at a crucial time like this.

589
00:35:49,150 --> 00:35:50,880
Have you found those two jerks?

590
00:35:51,190 --> 00:35:52,850
We're still looking for them.

591
00:35:55,030 --> 00:35:56,290
I can't be of much help.

592
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:58,690
Focus on your recovery.

593
00:35:59,230 --> 00:36:00,230
I need to recover,

594
00:36:00,510 --> 00:36:02,440
but the work still needs to be done.

595
00:36:02,960 --> 00:36:03,960
Take all the guys outside

596
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:04,820
with you later.

597
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:05,840
No way.

598
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:08,530
You need people around you
in this condition.

599
00:36:08,550 --> 00:36:09,480
Mr. Zhou,

600
00:36:10,590 --> 00:36:12,520
I can get the priorities straight.

601
00:36:12,670 --> 00:36:13,800
At a crucial time like this,

602
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:16,660
finding the phone
matters more than anything else.

603
00:36:20,440 --> 00:36:21,590
How about I find you a specialist

604
00:36:21,590 --> 00:36:23,050
in the provincial capital

605
00:36:23,230 --> 00:36:25,150
to get a second opinion
and avoid a misdiagnosis?

606
00:36:25,150 --> 00:36:26,190
Don't bother.

607
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:28,240
It's just a minor injury.

608
00:36:28,320 --> 00:36:30,450
Doctors in Sanjiangkou can handle it.

609
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:36,510
Bowen,

610
00:36:37,760 --> 00:36:38,680
caffeine

611
00:36:38,780 --> 00:36:40,380
comes from coffee cherries.

612
00:36:41,070 --> 00:36:43,440
So, every cause has an effect,

613
00:36:43,880 --> 00:36:45,590
and every effect has a cause.

614
00:36:50,070 --> 00:36:50,770
Bowen,

615
00:36:51,440 --> 00:36:52,840
Mr. Zhou means

616
00:36:53,110 --> 00:36:54,310
that in some matters,

617
00:36:54,630 --> 00:36:56,090
we are all in the same boat.

618
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:57,670
I'm very curious.

619
00:36:57,670 --> 00:36:59,030
Why did you go to Fenglingwan

620
00:36:59,030 --> 00:37:00,360
to drink and pick a fight

621
00:37:00,550 --> 00:37:01,920
right after I called you

622
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:04,220
and talked about the lost phone? Well...

623
00:37:04,360 --> 00:37:05,560
It's weird, isn't it?

624
00:37:12,070 --> 00:37:13,510
If my suspicion is wrong,

625
00:37:16,110 --> 00:37:18,370
I'll lose this hand of mine to you, Bowen.

626
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:20,040
But there's no knife.

627
00:37:20,400 --> 00:37:21,000
Yangyang.

628
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:22,540
Go find a scalpel.

629
00:37:22,920 --> 00:37:23,550
Jianren,

630
00:37:24,230 --> 00:37:25,960
come at me if you have a problem.

631
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:27,330
Don't scare my brother.

632
00:37:30,280 --> 00:37:31,840
And I must correct you.

633
00:37:33,040 --> 00:37:34,280
What do you mean by "in some matters,

634
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:35,810
we are all in the same boat"?

635
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:38,120
In all matters,

636
00:37:38,150 --> 00:37:39,670
we are all in the same boat.

637
00:37:40,880 --> 00:37:42,010
Am I right, Mr. Zhou?

638
00:37:42,110 --> 00:37:42,890
Exactly.

639
00:37:43,000 --> 00:37:44,530
Who are you trying to scare?

640
00:37:47,150 --> 00:37:47,880
Yes, Mentor.

641
00:37:49,920 --> 00:37:50,720
I see, Mentor.

642
00:37:53,000 --> 00:37:54,200
Don't worry, Mentor.

643
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:58,730
Chief Zhang, time for the meeting.

644
00:38:03,360 --> 00:38:04,160
What's wrong?

645
00:38:07,480 --> 00:38:09,480
Who on earth has got such a big mouth?

646
00:38:10,440 --> 00:38:11,960
The news about Li Qian getting injured
at Zhou Rong's place

647
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:13,760
has been spread to my mentor again.

648
00:38:13,760 --> 00:38:14,320
Not me.

649
00:38:23,100 --> 00:38:24,100
Sorry, Yangyang.

650
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:27,280
Mr. Zhou, why would you say that?

651
00:38:27,630 --> 00:38:29,190
Letting you see that scene just now,

652
00:38:29,190 --> 00:38:31,390
I owe you an apology as your big brother.

653
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:33,280
Please don't say that, Mr. Zhou.

654
00:38:34,190 --> 00:38:35,280
Are you also wondering

655
00:38:35,280 --> 00:38:36,840
how I could suspect your brother

656
00:38:36,840 --> 00:38:38,540
since we've known each other for 20 years?

657
00:38:38,540 --> 00:38:40,070
[Nurse Station]

658
00:38:40,540 --> 00:38:41,800
Actually, I also understand

659
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:44,070
that he doesn't want you
to know about our business.

660
00:38:44,070 --> 00:38:45,570
But this time,

661
00:38:45,880 --> 00:38:47,080
it's really serious.

662
00:38:47,630 --> 00:38:49,560
It's a matter of his life and death.

663
00:38:50,280 --> 00:38:51,140
But look at him.

664
00:38:51,190 --> 00:38:52,230
Even at a time like this,

665
00:38:52,230 --> 00:38:54,160
he still acts like he doesn't care.

666
00:38:55,880 --> 00:38:56,610
Mr. Zhou,

667
00:38:56,760 --> 00:38:58,320
may I ask what it is?

668
00:39:00,070 --> 00:39:00,880
Yesterday, two people

669
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:01,940
broke into my house

670
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:03,590
and stole a phone.

671
00:39:04,320 --> 00:39:05,400
That phone

672
00:39:05,670 --> 00:39:06,920
stores the only evidence

673
00:39:06,920 --> 00:39:08,850
that your brother killed Lu Zheng.

674
00:39:09,110 --> 00:39:10,170
Do you understand?

675
00:39:12,400 --> 00:39:13,670
But now his leg is injured.

676
00:39:13,670 --> 00:39:14,870
What should we do now?

677
00:39:15,440 --> 00:39:16,190
You may go back

678
00:39:16,190 --> 00:39:17,850
and take care of your brother.

679
00:39:20,030 --> 00:39:20,670
Go back.

680
00:39:32,510 --> 00:39:33,760
Bowen, why are you out of bed?

681
00:39:33,760 --> 00:39:34,760
Is your leg okay?

682
00:39:35,400 --> 00:39:37,330
I'm just getting my blood flowing.

683
00:39:38,000 --> 00:39:40,000
What's in that barrel?

684
00:39:40,150 --> 00:39:41,550
Didn't you think the hospital food

685
00:39:41,550 --> 00:39:42,150
tasted awful?

686
00:39:42,150 --> 00:39:43,880
I made some especially for you.

687
00:39:44,320 --> 00:39:45,400
Thank you.

688
00:39:46,630 --> 00:39:48,760
Do you think I dare to eat what you cook?

689
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:51,500
If you really want me to get well soon,

690
00:39:51,920 --> 00:39:53,580
buy me some more of these nuts.

691
00:39:56,400 --> 00:39:57,210
Is Zhou Rong

692
00:39:57,510 --> 00:39:58,960
very unhappy?

693
00:40:02,510 --> 00:40:03,440
Mr. Zhou told me

694
00:40:03,440 --> 00:40:05,300
that the phone you're looking for

695
00:40:05,320 --> 00:40:06,720
stores the only evidence

696
00:40:06,760 --> 00:40:08,160
that you killed Lu Zheng.

697
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,350
He even told you that?

698
00:40:11,190 --> 00:40:12,320
Is it true, brother?

699
00:40:20,230 --> 00:40:22,430
Zhou Rong is really getting desperate.

700
00:40:22,800 --> 00:40:23,230
Bowen,

701
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:25,820
I'll go help Mr. Zhou find that phone.

702
00:40:26,710 --> 00:40:27,240
Help who?

703
00:40:28,070 --> 00:40:28,800
He's crazy.

704
00:40:28,840 --> 00:40:29,900
Are you crazy, too?

705
00:40:30,150 --> 00:40:31,610
Zhou Rong is about to flee.

706
00:40:32,670 --> 00:40:33,360
Flee?

707
00:40:34,400 --> 00:40:35,770
Why would Mr. Zhou flee?

708
00:40:36,070 --> 00:40:37,270
Because he's scared.

709
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:40,400
When people are scared,
they just want to run away.

710
00:40:40,400 --> 00:40:41,550
Have you ever thought about

711
00:40:41,550 --> 00:40:43,210
what you'll do if he runs away?

712
00:40:43,230 --> 00:40:44,920
I don't know who wants to mess with him,

713
00:40:44,920 --> 00:40:47,320
but it definitely has nothing
to do with me.

714
00:40:47,670 --> 00:40:49,190
Then let me ask you a question.

715
00:40:49,190 --> 00:40:50,920
When did you change your phone?

716
00:40:51,320 --> 00:40:52,520
How would I remember?

717
00:40:53,440 --> 00:40:54,150
I remember.

718
00:40:55,030 --> 00:40:56,440
The day after Lu Zheng died,

719
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:57,770
you changed your phone.

720
00:40:59,630 --> 00:41:00,760
What Mr. Rong said is true.

721
00:41:00,760 --> 00:41:01,960
You killed Lu Zheng.

722
00:41:03,320 --> 00:41:04,400
Go tell the police.

723
00:41:04,440 --> 00:41:05,030
Go now.

724
00:41:06,550 --> 00:41:07,070
Bowen,

725
00:41:07,320 --> 00:41:08,960
we can't let Mr. Zhou run away.

726
00:41:08,960 --> 00:41:10,860
If he escapes and his phone
falls into the hands of the police,

727
00:41:10,860 --> 00:41:11,920
you'll be done for.

728
00:41:12,230 --> 00:41:14,250
Just don't meddle in the business,

729
00:41:14,590 --> 00:41:15,520
my dear brother.

730
00:41:16,190 --> 00:41:17,930
Just put your mind at ease.

731
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:19,130
Your brother

732
00:41:20,190 --> 00:41:22,190
will even get through this obstacle

733
00:41:22,190 --> 00:41:23,150
safe and sound.

734
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:26,550
Just don't worry.
